{
    "publish_date": "2013-03-27T15:12:57.000Z", 
    "score": 0.0, 
    "video_length": "PT7M21S", 
    "captions": [
        {
            "text": "This is where I live. I live in Kenya,", 
            "dur": "2.774", 
            "start": "12.982"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "at the south parts of the Nairobi National Park.", 
            "dur": "3.067", 
            "start": "15.756"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Those are my dad&#39;s cows at the back,", 
            "dur": "1.988", 
            "start": "18.823"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and behind the cows,", 
            "dur": "1.98", 
            "start": "20.811"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that&#39;s the Nairobi National Park.", 
            "dur": "2.304", 
            "start": "22.791"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Nairobi National Park is not fenced in the south widely,", 
            "dur": "3.505", 
            "start": "25.095"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "which means wild animals like zebras", 
            "dur": "3.462", 
            "start": "28.6"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "migrate out of the park freely.", 
            "dur": "3.921", 
            "start": "32.062"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So predators like lions follow them,", 
            "dur": "4.013", 
            "start": "35.983"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and this is what they do.", 
            "dur": "2.795", 
            "start": "39.996"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "They kill our livestock.", 
            "dur": "3.001", 
            "start": "42.791"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This is one of the cows which was killed at night,", 
            "dur": "2.447", 
            "start": "45.792"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and I just woke up in the morning and I found it dead,", 
            "dur": "4.04", 
            "start": "48.239"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and I felt so bad,", 
            "dur": "2.426", 
            "start": "52.279"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "because it was the only bull we had.", 
            "dur": "4.487", 
            "start": "54.705"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "My community, the Maasai, we believe that", 
            "dur": "2.787", 
            "start": "59.192"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "we came from heaven with all our animals and all the land", 
            "dur": "6.057", 
            "start": "61.979"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "for herding them, and that&#39;s why we value them so much.", 
            "dur": "3.775", 
            "start": "68.036"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So I grew up hating lions so much.", 
            "dur": "3.759", 
            "start": "71.811"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The morans are the warriors", 
            "dur": "3.053", 
            "start": "75.57"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "who protect our community and the livestock,", 
            "dur": "3.317", 
            "start": "78.623"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and they&#39;re also upset about this problem.", 
            "dur": "3.079", 
            "start": "81.94"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So they kill the lions.", 
            "dur": "3.005", 
            "start": "85.019"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s one of the six lions which were killed in Nairobi.", 
            "dur": "3.914", 
            "start": "88.024"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I think this is why the Nairobi National Park lions are few.", 
            "dur": "4.539", 
            "start": "91.938"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So a boy, from six to nine years old, in my community", 
            "dur": "4.961", 
            "start": "96.477"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "is responsible for his dad&#39;s cows,", 
            "dur": "2.874", 
            "start": "101.438"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and that&#39;s the same thing which happened to me.", 
            "dur": "3.13", 
            "start": "104.312"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So I had to find a way of solving this problem.", 
            "dur": "3.415", 
            "start": "107.442"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And the first idea I got was to use fire,", 
            "dur": "4.814", 
            "start": "110.857"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "because I thought lions were scared of fire.", 
            "dur": "3.793", 
            "start": "115.671"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But I came to realize that that didn&#39;t really help,", 
            "dur": "4.719", 
            "start": "119.464"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "because it was even helping the lions", 
            "dur": "2.609", 
            "start": "124.183"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to see through the cowshed.", 
            "dur": "3.511", 
            "start": "126.792"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So I didn&#39;t give up. I continued.", 
            "dur": "3.329", 
            "start": "130.303"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And a second idea I got was", 
            "dur": "2.64", 
            "start": "133.632"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to use a scarecrow.", 
            "dur": "2.067", 
            "start": "136.272"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I was trying to trick the lions", 
            "dur": "1.614", 
            "start": "138.339"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[into thinking] that I was standing near the cowshed.", 
            "dur": "2.907", 
            "start": "139.953"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But lions are very clever. (Laughter)", 
            "dur": "4.076", 
            "start": "142.86"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "They will come the first day and they see the scarecrow, and they go back,", 
            "dur": "4.446", 
            "start": "146.936"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but the second day, they&#39;ll come and they say,", 
            "dur": "3.274", 
            "start": "151.382"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "this thing is not moving here, it&#39;s always here. (Laughter)", 
            "dur": "3.11", 
            "start": "154.656"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So he jumps in and kills the animals.", 
            "dur": "3.237", 
            "start": "157.766"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So one night, I was walking around the cowshed with a torch,", 
            "dur": "3.953", 
            "start": "161.003"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and that day, the lions didn&#39;t come.", 
            "dur": "3.843", 
            "start": "164.956"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I discovered that lions are afraid of a moving light.", 
            "dur": "4.558", 
            "start": "168.799"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So I had an idea.", 
            "dur": "2.573", 
            "start": "173.357"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Since I was a small boy,", 
            "dur": "2.31", 
            "start": "175.93"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I used to work in my room for the whole day,", 
            "dur": "3.258", 
            "start": "178.24"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and I even took apart my mom&#39;s new radio,", 
            "dur": "3.106", 
            "start": "181.498"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and that day she almost killed me,", 
            "dur": "1.818", 
            "start": "184.604"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but I learned a lot about electronics. (Laughter)", 
            "dur": "6.254", 
            "start": "186.422"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So I got an old car battery,", 
            "dur": "3.36", 
            "start": "192.676"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "an indicator box. It&#39;s a small device found in a motorcycle,", 
            "dur": "3.79", 
            "start": "196.036"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and it helps motorists when they want to turn right or left. It blinks.", 
            "dur": "5.051", 
            "start": "199.826"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I got a switch where I can switch on the lights, on and off.", 
            "dur": "4.554", 
            "start": "204.877"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And that&#39;s a small torch from a broken flashlight.", 
            "dur": "4.828", 
            "start": "209.431"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So I set up everything.", 
            "dur": "2.881", 
            "start": "214.259"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "As you can see, the solar panel charges the battery,", 
            "dur": "3.224", 
            "start": "217.14"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and the battery supplies the power", 
            "dur": "2.121", 
            "start": "220.364"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to the small indicator box. I call it a transformer.", 
            "dur": "3.055", 
            "start": "222.485"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And the indicator box makes the lights flash.", 
            "dur": "4.721", 
            "start": "225.54"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "As you can see, the bulbs face outside,", 
            "dur": "3.751", 
            "start": "230.261"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "because that&#39;s where the lions come from.", 
            "dur": "2.488", 
            "start": "234.012"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And that&#39;s how it looks to lions when they come at night.", 
            "dur": "4.064", 
            "start": "236.5"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The lights flash and trick", 
            "dur": "2.728", 
            "start": "240.564"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the lions into thinking I was walking around the cowshed,", 
            "dur": "1.942", 
            "start": "243.292"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but I was sleeping in my bed.", 
            "dur": "1.926", 
            "start": "245.234"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Laughter)", 
            "dur": "2.74", 
            "start": "247.16"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Applause)", 
            "dur": "1.669", 
            "start": "249.9"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Thanks.", 
            "dur": "5.595", 
            "start": "251.569"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So I set it up in my home two years ago,", 
            "dur": "4.276", 
            "start": "257.164"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and since then, we have never experienced any problem with lions.", 
            "dur": "3.32", 
            "start": "261.44"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And my neighboring homes heard about this idea.", 
            "dur": "4.012", 
            "start": "264.76"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "One of them was this grandmother.", 
            "dur": "2.464", 
            "start": "268.772"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "She had a lot of her animals being killed by lions,", 
            "dur": "4.276", 
            "start": "271.236"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and she asked me if I could put the lights for her.", 
            "dur": "2.134", 
            "start": "275.512"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I said, &quot;Yes.&quot;", 
            "dur": "1.278", 
            "start": "277.646"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So I put the lights. You can see at the back, those are the lion lights.", 
            "dur": "4.6", 
            "start": "278.924"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Since now, I&#39;ve set up seven homes around my community,", 
            "dur": "3.416", 
            "start": "283.524"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and they&#39;re really working.", 
            "dur": "2.225", 
            "start": "286.94"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And my idea is also being used now all over Kenya", 
            "dur": "5.18", 
            "start": "289.165"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "for scaring other predators like hyenas, leopards,", 
            "dur": "5.113", 
            "start": "294.345"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and it&#39;s also being used", 
            "dur": "2.235", 
            "start": "299.458"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to scare elephants away from people&#39;s farms.", 
            "dur": "4.045", 
            "start": "301.693"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Because of this invention, I was lucky to get a scholarship", 
            "dur": "3.04", 
            "start": "305.738"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "in one of the best schools in Kenya,", 
            "dur": "2.65", 
            "start": "308.778"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Brookhouse International School,", 
            "dur": "1.907", 
            "start": "311.428"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and I&#39;m really excited about this.", 
            "dur": "2.927", 
            "start": "313.335"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "My new school now is coming in and helping", 
            "dur": "3.85", 
            "start": "316.262"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "by fundraising and creating an awareness.", 
            "dur": "4.532", 
            "start": "320.112"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I even took my friends back to my community,", 
            "dur": "5.283", 
            "start": "324.644"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and we&#39;re installing the lights to the homes", 
            "dur": "3.197", 
            "start": "329.927"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "which don&#39;t have [any], and I&#39;m teaching them how to put them.", 
            "dur": "4.649", 
            "start": "333.124"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So one year ago, I was just a boy in the savanna grassland", 
            "dur": "3.897", 
            "start": "337.773"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "herding my father&#39;s cows,", 
            "dur": "1.674", 
            "start": "341.67"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and I used to see planes flying over,", 
            "dur": "2.954", 
            "start": "343.344"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and I told myself that one day, I&#39;ll be there inside.", 
            "dur": "4.211", 
            "start": "346.298"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And here I am today.", 
            "dur": "3.088", 
            "start": "350.509"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I got a chance to come by plane for my first time for TED.", 
            "dur": "5.936", 
            "start": "353.597"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So my big dream is to become an aircraft engineer and pilot when I grow up.", 
            "dur": "5.436", 
            "start": "359.533"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I used to hate lions, but now because my invention", 
            "dur": "3.694", 
            "start": "364.969"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "is saving my father&#39;s cows and the lions,", 
            "dur": "3.318", 
            "start": "368.663"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "we are able to stay with the lions without any conflict.", 
            "dur": "3.7", 
            "start": "371.981"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Ash\u00ea ol\u00ean. It means in my language, thank you very much.", 
            "dur": "3.22", 
            "start": "375.681"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Applause)", 
            "dur": "10.9", 
            "start": "378.901"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Chris Anderson: You have no idea how exciting it is", 
            "dur": "2.301", 
            "start": "393.381"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to hear a story like yours.", 
            "dur": "2.111", 
            "start": "395.682"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So you got this scholarship.\nRichard Turere: Yep.", 
            "dur": "2.036", 
            "start": "397.793"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "CA: You&#39;re working on other electrical inventions.", 
            "dur": "2.577", 
            "start": "399.829"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "What&#39;s the next one on your list?", 
            "dur": "1.858", 
            "start": "402.406"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "RT: My next invention is,", 
            "dur": "2.674", 
            "start": "404.264"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I want to make an electric fence.\nCA: Electric fence?", 
            "dur": "2.582", 
            "start": "406.938"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "RT: But I know electric fences are already invented,", 
            "dur": "2.161", 
            "start": "409.52"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but I want to make mine.", 
            "dur": "2.237", 
            "start": "411.681"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Laughter)", 
            "dur": "2.091", 
            "start": "413.918"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "CA: You already tried it once, right, and you --\nRT: I tried it before,", 
            "dur": "3.17", 
            "start": "416.009"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but I stopped because it gave me a shock. (Laughter)", 
            "dur": "6.757", 
            "start": "419.179"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "CA: In the trenches. Richard Turere, you are something else.", 
            "dur": "3.326", 
            "start": "425.936"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We&#39;re going to cheer you on every step of the way, my friend.", 
            "dur": "2.968", 
            "start": "429.262"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Thank you so much.\nRT: Thank you. (Applause)", 
            "dur": "3.557", 
            "start": "432.23"
        }
    ], 
